<TEXT>
the combination of a volatile star and a 
director of international renown might seem potentially explosive 
but jessica lange and constantin costagavras claim the expected 
fireworks didnt happen in their collaboration on music box 
after her disastrous debut in king kong lange began taking 
charge of her career she has reportedly clashed with directors 
over interpretations of her film roles and has developed and 
produced her own projects such as country 
costagavras is known as the uncompromising greekborn director 
of such politicallythemed films as z missing and 
betrayed music box deals with guilt from the holocaust 
i had input as far as the development of the character says 
the actress who plays a chicago lawyer defending her father 
against charges he murdered jews in his native hungary 
i wasnt involved at a production level i had such respect 
and confidence in costa that i didnt feel the need to get in there 
and make my opinions known i agreed with what he was doing which 
made the filmmaking much easier for me its difficult when youre 
not in agreement with how the film is being made you have to 
expend a lot of energy arguing or opposing the way things are 
happening 
in this case everybody was in sync but its rare 
she is strong and extremely nice costagavras said about 
his star it was a big pleasure because the relationship 
developed little by little getting very close as we spoke about 
the character in a very intimate way i think it was quite a unique 
experience to me she looks a little distant but shes absolutely 
not 
in one of her infrequent interviews lange was asked if she 
encountered any resentment because a star insisted on making her 
opinions known 
she laughed and replied i suppose there was some of that im 
certainly not the first person to do that and i wont be the last 
sometimes youre just an actress for hire you go in and do your 
part and thats it at other times your commitment is deeper than 
that 
lange approached her music box role with her usual 
thoroughness hanging out in courtrooms and reading endless legal 
briefs ultimately you can observe behavior she said but 
when you get down to playing it it all has to come from the 
character 
but i learned a lot about legal proceedings its a very 
tricky business one thing i learned about law is that its not 
synonymous with truth they do not exist sidebyside which is too 
bad because originally i think thats what it was meant to be now 
so much of it is rhetoric tricks and manipulation 
the 40yearold lange reigns as one of the five mostindemand 
